text:
Look, look, Producer!
How is it!?

Right!? It's so cool!
Rushing here was worth it.
The costume wouldn't run away, though.

But, you know, I wanted to try it on as soon as possible.
The matching costumes for everyone at 283PRO.

Wearing matching costumes like this,
it makes me feel like we've come a long way!

That's right. It's thanks to you working hard
in illumine, Meguru.

But, but, it's not "just me", it's everyone at 283PRO!
And of course, you too, Producer!
